 To first order,
 taking the flow in infinitesimal time is just calculating the velocity vector at the point and moving in the direction of the tip.
 In other words,
 (visualizing vectors as infinitesimal arrows) we may visualize 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{\varepsilon}^{*}\omega$
